the show was set in cleveland , ohio , and revolved around the retail office and home life of " everyman " drew carey , a fictionalized version of the actor.http://www.nytimes.com/1998/10/25/tv/signoff - now-roasting-and-toasting-drew-carey.html   the show was created by carey , who had both stand - up comedy and writing experience , and bruce helford , who was once a writer for roseanne .

